    "description": "<strong>注意:DEMO时长为40-60分钟左右,而正式版流程为2-3小时,作为故事作品我其实对于开不开放demo有些纠结.不过考虑九月就正式发售,应该没事</strong><br><br><strong>另外不用担心,DEMO内进度存档在正式版可以沿用。</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160350/extras/73768b828c98babfce625445709f573f.avif?t=1723687261\" width=128 height=64 /></span> <br><br><strong>芙兰杂感记录</strong> 是款2d像素剧情游戏.<br><br>一个寻求答案的故事<br><br>所有人。<br><br><br>-------------------<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160350/extras/0496ffb3a0797a73e47e2a174107efdc.avif?t=1723687261\" width=128 height=64 /></span><br><br>芙兰杂感记录以剧情为主,其中存在一些惊悚表现.<br><br>游戏主要玩法非常简单:您可以通过移动来逐渐解决谜题,理解整个故事. <br><br>当然,为了防止可能的乏味体验,游戏也配备了故事记录与简单的推理系统,相信您足够在这个故事中获得完美的体验!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160350/extras/9d7b0731631078aa40e171e09c744739.avif?t=1723687261\" width=614 height=342 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160350/extras/fd1e53c16ca0e765b09e67501d8c2189.avif?t=1723687261\" width=614 height=342 /></span><br><br><br>-------------------<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160350/extras/182195f5dd07577d73307f48f621d821.avif?t=1723687261\" width=128 height=64 /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160350/extras/6e14c03da63274abb0fc98b213ec31ae.apng?t=1723687261\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160350/extras/6e14c03da63274abb0fc98b213ec31ae.poster.avif?t=1723687261\" class=\"bb_img\" width=237 height=267 /></picture></span><br><strong>芙兰</strong>:一个仇恨过去,渴望答案的吸血鬼少女。<br><br>在经历了混乱的噩梦日记事件后,她选择了逃离自己熟知的一切。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160350/extras/99bee1d8325d1ff3fd01dfc42fce720d.poster.avif?t=1723687261\" width=237 height=267 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160350/extras/99bee1d8325d1ff3fd01dfc42fce720d.webm?t=1723687261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>阿猫</strong>:一只在噩梦日记事件中来到芙兰身边的猫又。<br><br>另一个世界的&quot;被遗忘者&quot;.<br><br>此外游戏也有另外值得圈点的特色:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>独特像素风格的2D卷轴推进式短篇故事.<br></li><li>音乐外全部由作者独自制作的游戏内容.<br></li><li>熠熠生辉的故事内核,但是迫于无能而表达不好的菜鸟作者</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160350/extras/016b507ded625846219cc1702677f2dd.poster.avif?t=1723687261\" width=614 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160350/extras/016b507ded625846219cc1702677f2dd.webm?t=1723687261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160350/extras/016b507ded625846219cc1702677f2dd.mp4?t=1723687261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >来一杯?照常?</h2><br>-------------------<br><strong>特别留言:</strong><br>假如你对Geism的任何作品感兴趣,但是苦于什么原因无法购买,我都会无条件提供离线版本,未来任何作品都是这样。<br><strong>关于Geism:</strong><br>游戏收入的绝大百分比,除了为维持未来可能的开发费用以外,其余都会投入Geism未来支持的工益事业中。<br>且Geism官网上线后,支出,游戏相关的收入,会全部公开;以及上述的作品离线版本下载。<br>此留言的核心想法在未来每个Geism发布的作品都会标注。<br>如果Geism做了任何违背这一原则的事情,请务必羞辱并加以指正。<br>(简单注明:截至到杂感记录发布,Geism暂时是作者一人,水平能力极其有限,请不要抱有过多期待,共勉。",
